data.description: Motivated Sellers! What a view from the moment you enter through the foyer area. Wide open water views… not to mention the walk in pantry room off the kitchen! Some amazing features here in this home located in a resort style, low maintenance community calledHeron's Glen Country Club. Enjoy expansive waterviews from this custom built 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in guard gated community with resort style community amenities at your disposal. Chef's kitchen boasts granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, bar seating and the most amazing walk in butler's pantry with floor to ceiling cabinetry! The bedrooms boast large closets with one of them offering a very desirable extended walk in closet space. What a dream come true! Brand new roof just installed in 2023, as well as all openings being hurricane protected for your peace of mind! Situated overlooking the 2nd hole Tee you're able to relish in the wildlife, the waterviews, or the golfers going by in the distance. This is a pet friendly, golf cart friendly, active community! Golf memberships are optional, just pay as you play! Community amenities include the most amenity rich gated community in the area w/Championship 18-hole golf course, 6 Har-Tru & 6 pickleball courts, new fitness center, bocce/shuffleboard, resort style pool/spa, restaurant & bar! Residents may rent their home for no less than 30 days at a time. Up to 3 pets are welcome, with no breed restrictions. This home is conveniently located just 7 minutes from downtown, 15 minutes from Punta Gorda Airport, 30 minutes from Fort Myers Airport and minutes from I-75. Heron's Glen HOA fees also cover the lawn mowing for each home, as well as basic internet and cable too!
